title: [SOLVED]820-2610 - Won't turn on
message:
Guys,

I know this board is old, but i need to fix!
The costumer said, after start gets gray screen and another day the computer just don't turn on anymore.


I get:
PPBUS_G3H (schematics is 6v but i get 8.2v)
PPBUS_CPU_IMVP_ISNS
PPDCIN_G3H
PP3V42_G3H

SMC_RESET_L - 3.4v

I don't get:
PP5V_S3


I replaced C7771 and works.

But the client bring back exactly the same problem.
So, i check C7771 pin 1 and i get 0.34v. Something fuck up again this capacitor.

Do you guys can help me out?
